'''导管内乳头状黏液性肿瘤'''（intraductal papillary mucinous neoplasm， IPMN）是一种在胰管细胞内发生的[[贅生物|肿瘤]]。IPMN会产生黏液<ref name="JHUFAQ">{{Cite web|title=Intraductal Papillary Mucinous Neoplasms of the Pancreas|url=http://pathology.jhu.edu/pancreas/IPMN.php|accessdate=7 September 2009|publisher=[[Johns_Hopkins_University|Johns Hopkins University]]|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204201720/https://pathology.jhu.edu/pancreas/IPMN.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>，这种黏液会形成{{le|胰腺囊肿|Pancreatic cyst}}。<ref name="Campbell2015">{{Cite journal|title=Imaging patterns of intraductal papillary mucinous neoplasms of the pancreas: an illustrated discussion of the International Consensus Guidelines for the Management of IPMN|last=Campbell|first=NM|last2=Katz|first2=SS|date=March 2015|journal=Abdominal Imaging|issue=3|doi=10.1007/s00261-014-0236-4|volume=40|pages=663–77|pmid=25219664|last3=Escalon|first3=JG|last4=Do|first4=RK}}</ref>虽然IPMN是一种[[良性肿瘤|良性肿瘤]]，但IPMN有可能发展为[[胰腺癌|胰腺癌]]。因此，IPMN被视为一种{{le|癌前状态|Precancerous condition}}。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Precancerous conditions of the pancreas - Canadian Cancer Society|url=http://www.cancer.ca/en/cancer-information/cancer-type/pancreatic/pancreatic-cancer/precancerous-conditions/?region=on|accessdate=5 November 2017|work=www.cancer.ca|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214140416/https://www.cancer.ca/en/cancer-information/cancer-type/pancreatic/pancreatic-cancer/precancerous-conditions/?region=on|dead-url=no}}</ref>

